response.overview: UMass Private Investigator Vik Jaisingh found a client; he found a case; but can he find the coin? In this second installment of his docu-series, he picks up the trail from right where he left it. Old friends; new friends; purple frogs and party-planning. Will Vik fulfill his duty? Will the world care? And is that even important? All that can be said is: do not eat at the Walmart Subway.
response.title: Vik Finds A Coin
